episodes.title: LORI VALLOW: Not a Lawyer, But Played One in Court Today
episodes.description: Lori Vallow hijacked her own trial and argued like she was on a Netflix legal drama. In this episode, Ashleigh Banfield breaks down Lori Vallow's courtroom theatrics.
